Package fr.umlv.chathack.resources.readers

Class FrameReader

java.lang.Object
fr.umlv.chathack.resources.readers.FrameReader
All Implemented Interfaces:
Reader
public class FrameReader
extends Object
implements Reader
This class is used to process the data in the ByteBuffer bb. The state is used to know what to do when the method process is called. The state WAITING_OPCODE mean that we are still waiting for the first byte of the frame. As soon as you got it, the method will process the data of the corresponding reader. the map is only use to associate an opCode to a reader. When the frame is totally receive the Frame will be created. And the method return the Frame corresponding to the data processed.
